s="nav__breadcrumb--item"><a class="breadcrumb--link" href="/en"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">Home</span></a><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li><li class="nav__breadcrumb--item lastItem"><span class="nav__breadcrumb--text">404</span><span class="nav__breadcrumb--divider"></span></li></ol></div><div class="lead__content container"><div class="row justify-content-md-center"><div class="col-12 col-md-10 col-lg-8"><div class="main__content--headline"><h1>Page not found (404)</h1></div><div class="ce__lead"><div class="ce__lead--content"><div class="ce__lead--text">The requested page does not exist.</div></div></div></div></div></div><main class="main__content"><div class="neos-contentcollection"><div class="container teaserGroup teaserGroup__3col" data-internezz-teaser--teasergroup><div class="row" data-internezzo-teaser--teasergroup-teasercontainer><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="7cd9973a-60b2-4433-80a3-146c56ff2fa4"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{'id':'a3a1935a-871d-456a-ac3a-7667d544ab7e','name':'NPL_Step-Up__SWISS_CONTACT_FISH_POLUTRY_FARM_%2810%29.jpeg','title':'Nepal Step Up Project Poultry Farm','alt':'Nepal Step Up Project Poultry Farm','hash':'a167193c7ad53069988b6afa3a8a04324e28645b','maxwidth':'2400','originalwidth':'2400','originalheight':'1599'}" style="padding-bottom: 66.625%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Home</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Swisscontact was founded over 60 years ago by representatives of the Swiss private sector. Collaboration with the private sector is in our DNA. We leverage its capital to foster economic growth that is environmentally and socially sound, and we believe that together we can achieve more.<br />
<br />
 </div></div><a href="/en" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="3f46a1be-79a2-48cd-9be8-daf8c7f1ff6a"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/projects"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{'id':'eae4672f-5c2e-47bc-a94f-934385f4b233','name':'Prodi_listrik_Morowali-2019__%28175%29_%281%29.jpg','title':'','alt':'','hash':'b51715e672c2dcaf4618515a43282ec20ac877c8','maxwidth':'5184','originalwidth':'5184','originalheight':'3454'}" style="padding-bottom: 66.628086419753%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">Projects</div><div class="teaser__box--text">Our development work focuses on private sector-led, sustainable economic development with improved quality of life for all in developing and emerging countries.&nbsp;</span><span>A key focus is to strengthen</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>the skills of individuals and foster the competitiveness of companies.</span><span> </span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;</div></div><a href="/en/projects" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div><div class="teaser__element teaser__3col col-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4" data-internezzo-teaser--uniqueTeasedNodeIdentifier="03c439bf-db4d-493c-b6d2-cb07ec251bb1"><div class="teaser__element--wrapper"><div class="teaser__image"><a href="/en/news"><div class="img-ari--responsive" data-ari-params="{'id':'914cbd4d-abdd-4710-8a29-1b3e12e7e4bf','name':'IMG_7055.jpg','title':'','alt':'','hash':'0174e062b3dc7887379486a9b3e7e4bc73d4add5','maxwidth':'5616','originalwidth':'5616','originalheight':'3742'}" style="padding-bottom: 66.631054131054%"></div></a></div><div class="teaser__box"><div class="teaser__box--title">News</div><div class="teaser__box--text"></div></div><a href="/en/news" class="teaser--link" title></a></div></div></div></div></div></main><div class="share__content container"><div cla